3a8923977701d455e45","tid":1456040,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pxK3T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pxK3T.jpg&h=1666b05a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKcO2Qy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKcO2Qy.jpg&h=dd56ad4d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mryR0Cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmryR0Cd.jpg&h=f64d4e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"795ea6758ef7f450e94ae205ab015fc8d83f818e","tid":1456040,"uid":259046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"啲狗咩都做得出 吾好諗 快啲走"},{"pid":"99a3d28bbf10b9448926468590aa81d4ff496c62","tid":1456040,"uid":56469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"更新：1722 運輸及房屋局局長陳帆於記者會上定性今天機場集會為非法集結 #港台直播<br />\n<br />\n所以狗隻係絕對有「合法」理由去清場，而佢地都絕對做得出，手足們，請走，我仲想係煲底除低口罩同大家見一面，好嗎？"},{"pid":"fa71638efb8cc3ea49b99d97a7ff490015632fd2","tid":1456040,"uid":287582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:43:36.000Z","msg":"快走  唔好再諗   <br />\n唔值得留"},{"pid":"445ac301a9715f2f16d52a8be2e3c92297273710","tid":1456040,"uid":291372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"如果機場出事～今晚個夢應該有噴火龍"},{"pid":"c88c8e86e76917132f4f4f9fd238b1cb526eab1a","tid":1456040,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲上到網嘅現場手足<br />\n通知下隔離上唔到網嘅手足<br />\n去setting轉用3G<br />\n喺網絡大擠塞嘅情況下會易啲上到網</span>"},{"pid":"b0588eb833186221a392b2983ccc58a3557f3826","tid":1456040,"uid":113784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:44:31.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n留低有咩做？？自己問下自己。<br />\n<br />\n到時機場回復運作咪再入過囉，更加唔好講夜晚收工接力的手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa59f6f0d61cc0325c2e0cc2fb94bdc017136bc9","tid":1456040,"uid":195211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"走啦蠢"},{"pid":"50a684b7a6860182c25f21d9cf622b9b18b88b0b","tid":1456040,"uid":275616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fdbc0942bbf2e470ca87b8d55e3b651ca079b5a","tid":1456040,"uid":275616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:42:08.000Z","msg":"一手料<br />\n<br />\n見到警方裝甲車駛往機場方向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"係喺北大嶼山公路見到的<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好畀機會佢重演六四好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c396b4fbc8d4f1ae7c8074e8e166c9a2af41da","tid":1456040,"uid":288025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:45:15.000Z","msg":"大家快啲離開，好心痛"},{"pid":"86545a90d9655f24434b1868355e2b94f804ac31","tid":1456040,"uid":56469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"[現場消息] 1745 轉自朋友：機場熄左燈同埋冷氣 冇車走既請參考以下選項：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.入番東涌坐船離開去屯門<br />\n2.有Disney 年票入左去先<br />\n3.昂坪360未關，上左去大佛先<br />\n4.入梅窩再坐船番港島</span>"},{"pid":"70226cc796c8b6a117d1a65fe359e5c2044a7187","tid":1456040,"uid":303002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"053f55c0bf947507eaee7df7bf1c2f146f85e228","tid":1456040,"uid":98766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"Be water ar 各位手足"},{"pid":"98a78805944d2d8bbaeaf9055f46bd4f111317d2","tid":1456040,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:47:17.000Z","msg":"【航界一手】香港空域暫時關閉直至另行通知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1455153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1455153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請置頂 請置頂  急急急  機場快線會停<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1455649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1455649</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日目標已達到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足be water勿送頭"},{"pid":"18a4bdd28f89535555ee70e361ff3bbbff2da2d0","tid":1456040,"uid":289177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:47:51.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n認同成功癱瘓機場運作，目的已達到。可留待明天再戰！<br />\n經過811，真係唔想再見到有義士送死，即刻走！！！"},{"pid":"264327566be2c64b6348a810fb53d3af666d532a","tid":1456040,"uid":56469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"自推，救得一個得一個，唔好落單，走！"},{"pid":"cccf855aeed80106932b63677b00160addc22ed2","tid":1456040,"uid":258584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"快啲走 求下大家"},{"pid":"9c6d3c9a0d42886b0861f1b74c75f68966398ecc","tid":1456040,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:49:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f100f0f0b53875a8696f13edbeca9db33d97cf7","tid":1456040,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df15b36c18dc1b9bc3b0f8b937a7d3140317894","tid":1456040,"uid":56469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"再更新：<br />\n<br />\n#機場 <br />\n最後更新：1742<br />\n經東涌離開機場：<br />\nS1/S56/S64-&gt;E31-&gt;荃灣<br />\nS56-&gt;船-&gt;屯門(尾班船已開)<br />\nS1/S56/S64-&gt;東涌綫<br />\n<br />\n經賣豬仔大橋：<br />\nB4-&gt;B5-&gt;東涌綫<br />\nT2往賣豬仔大橋A線-&gt;出市區A線<br />\n<br />\n經愉景灣離開機場：<br />\nDB02R-&gt;船-&gt;中環（DB02R已暫停服務)<br />\nS1/S56/S64-&gt;DB01R-&gt;船-&gt;中環<br />\n<br />\n經梅窩離開機場：<br />\nS1/S56/S64-&gt;3M-&gt;船-&gt;中環<br />\nA35-&gt;船-&gt;中環 A35最快將於1815喺機場開出"},{"pid":"1d2aa30498f6c38d70f7c2957b777fd1062541e9","tid":1456040,"uid":38533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4315e9e4f80969ef3fcc4d2e8006bce4e89ea8c","tid":1456040,"uid":56469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:51:36.000Z","msg":"再推，請馬上離開／叫朋友離開機場：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXRDFE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXRDFE4.jpg&h=c2df568d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6e6a64cfc6651b3f0a85eb4567a030a0798a7b3","tid":1456040,"uid":251810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"中point 即刻走唔好送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2c1a88216e71c6c49ef88ef468a0efbd4f8a1e","tid":1456040,"uid":236234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b186ef23148714f803c2f3eb149d12705b8d798","tid":1456040,"uid":56469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"我本身早有打算收工去機場，但成件事太鬼之餘，而家留低亦都冇任何實際作用，容我盡量簡短分析：<br />\n<br />\n點解一開始要入機場，目的就係想<strong>癱瘓機場運作</strong>。<br />\n而家已經成功做到呢一樣野，大部份航班取消，機場番工嘅人都已經準備收工／已收工，大量狗隻都已經去左機場，可以話係完全成功，冇需要更加冇必要再留係機場，此其一。<br />\n<br />\n其二，大量消息話機場會逐步封鎖，到時最基本會斷哂訊號、交通，最差既情況係警察做咩都冇人知，都唔會有傳媒可以報導。簡單啲講，<strong>佢地真係會有能力做到「64冇死人」</strong>，然後一大班手足就去左送頭，講緊可能唔止係畀人拉或者嚴重受傷，甚至係死。<br />\n<br />\n第三，今日大家「和理飛」，輕裝上陣或者冇gear嘅佔大多數，當尋晚個女仔都可以畀人射穿眼罩，今日大家得個口罩既時候，死傷只會更慘烈。<br />\n<br />\n補充：唔好同我講咩警察唔敢做呢樣做嗰樣，希望大家<strong>唔好再嘗試用常理</strong>去分析呢班人既行為，點解叫佢地做「狗」，唔係得個名，而係佢地做緊既野正正就好似d癲狗一樣，所謂警例、所謂道德、所謂正義，對佢地黎講已經蕩然無存。<br />\n<br />\n我知道自己人微言輕，但懇請大家在場見字既，請馬上離開現場；唔係現場既，馬上通知朋友離開機場，<strong>不受傷、不被捕</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">P.S. 如果大家本身諗住去機場，但而家唔去機場又唔知道去邊既話，我諗住同幾個朋友入去東涌欣賞下港豬澳大橋，假如狗隻係機場執法，都可以馬上去聲援，鍚下春袋，慰勞下一班勞苦功高嘅警犬。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e683a842214302842e4fb9d77b53e83c44543c5e","tid":1456040,"uid":180905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f04462dd9977a55d639e5ec7168dc42b245f0f3c","tid":1456040,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"推 走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903c06fc2fc55aec4f09fe047848096b82ffcfc3","tid":1456040,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"逆向思維 咩人最想人留?<br />\n<br />\n即走阿屌"},{"pid":"3c158e61da745e57498d6fb8b6bfc71952cbc879","tid":1456040,"uid":279927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"趁仍有遊客，一齊走安全！"},{"pid":"fa1cae084b81955dd9b2ca10131b88d3e54932d9","tid":1456040,"uid":19209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"小心帶風向"},{"pid":"e0fbd0c783af21ce094f9cdca1fb0190b49a7ee4","tid":1456040,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"其實我唔認同搞到機場shut down。<br />\n因為機場，我覺得主要目的係輸出革命。對外界宣傳。搞到冇旅客係本未倒置。<br />\n但點都好，呢獲野係唔值得送頭"},{"pid":"2b4eb733f1b9f1a3d3219b04d68dcab1212b28e4","tid":1456040,"uid":83335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:02:32.000Z","msg":"呢個post咁多p牌叫走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77b7ceef1065a5d3fa036070e5cdc6df4fe848b","tid":1456040,"uid":209893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:12:55.000Z","msg":"走啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />封死左就幾多人都冇撚用<br />\n唔想再見到有手足犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2cbc3b6652ff942997f270f0d4f627f53b98a1","tid":1456040,"uid":32861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:14:48.000Z","msg":"6月到依家你仲同政府講道理 講法律？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2019仲留守任何地方？<br />\n<br />\n要守既只有一個地方-香港<br />\n<br />\n2014仲留守唔夠咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉場</span></span>"}]}